Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.43,0:00:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風力操作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.34,0:00:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  風車在逆向旋轉？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.52,0:00:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  我有聽說過
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.22,0:00:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發電機的馬達受到特殊電波的干擾後會旋轉起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.53,0:00:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那些傢伙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.07,0:00:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋  但這又是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.80,0:01:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些風車也不是在隨便旋轉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.57,0:01:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是為了擾亂我的計算式而有指揮地…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.14,0:01:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙看到的畫面通過網絡…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.97,0:01:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滅了你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.45,0:01:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想
Comment: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.55,0:03:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是無法理解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.94,0:03:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躺在那邊的下三濫  還有你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.00,0:03:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼都要保護一個人偶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.57,0:03:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們只是仿製得粗製濫造的次品
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.98,0:03:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界上最討厭她的不應該是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看見和自己長得一模一樣的人被幹掉覺得不爽？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.03,0:03:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不會就因為這個理由就拚死拚活的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.70,0:04:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不允許有人比自己先成為絕對能力者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.70,0:04:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(420,332)\fs16\fsp6}Level6
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.63,0:04:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是對作為真正引起這個實驗的源頭的一種贖罪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.56,0:04:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對「神的頭腦」沒有任何興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.00,0:04:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不認為這麼做就能為自己贖罪了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.19,0:04:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.69,0:04:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她們是我的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.03,0:04:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.00,0:04:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我知道事到如今我已經沒有這資格了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.43,0:04:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  現在能允許我站在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.21,0:04:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…  好…  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.02,0:05:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會再讓任何一個人死去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.83,0:05:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  我還以為你要說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.37,0:05:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是演姐妹溫情劇啊  真無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.84,0:05:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不讓任何一個人死？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.02,0:05:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別得意忘形了  你這二流貨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.89,0:05:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們根本連阻擋我都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.16,0:05:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟檢查視力只能測到2.0是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.56,0:05:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為學園都市最高的等級只有5
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.97,0:05:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是沒辦法才忍受排在這一等級的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.96,0:05:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太麻煩了  就讓我把你們一起解決了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.14,0:06:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.03,0:06:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今為止我都殺了多少人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.36,0:06:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼做會讓人類徹底損壞我是再清楚不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.04,0:06:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都那樣了不可能再站得起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.01,0:06:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.67,0:06:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是個命硬的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.31,0:06:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算風能不能使用了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.48,0:06:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要指尖稍稍碰一下就能完成致命一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.48,0:06:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.91,0:07:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在是…太有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.28,0:07:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把牙關咬緊了  最強
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.47,0:07:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這個最弱可是有點疼的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.87,0:07:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.95,0:07:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這傢伙不會倒下？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.15,0:07:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護…人偶？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.83,0:07:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就差一步就能得到絕對的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.97,0:07:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…我會…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.49,0:08:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個能力總有一天會與整個世界為敵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.52,0:08:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能真的會將一切都毀滅殆盡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.23,0:08:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  只要進化到比「最強」更強
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.63,0:08:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定就會有什麼改變
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.14,0:08:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此要遵循計劃  完成實驗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.22,0:08:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小白鼠  人偶  克隆人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.35,0:08:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然能力會產生鬥爭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.21,0:08:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  只要成為讓人產生不了戰鬥想法的絕對的存在就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.85,0:08:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話…總有一天又能…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.63,0:08:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.29,0:09:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不用再讓任何人…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.52,0:09:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹們也是在努力地…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.15,0:09:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她們是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.85,0:09:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.10,0:09:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底在搞什麼鬼啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.32,0:10:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.53,0:10:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.19,0:10:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我進來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.68,0:10:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在睡覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.06,0:10:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然真的把學園都市的第一位給打倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.86,0:10:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是有多變態啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.65,0:11:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  吵醒你了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.35,0:11:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是探病的曲奇餅乾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.84,0:11:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在百貨店特意選了一個貴的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.33,0:11:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該會很好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.13,0:11:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有就是我覺得必須要對你說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.35,0:11:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.24,0:11:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起曲奇餅乾  果然還是親手做的最好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.07,0:11:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底期待著我是什麼形象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.59,0:11:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.55,0:11:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是笨手笨腳的人笨拙且努力地做出破破爛爛的曲奇餅乾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.80,0:11:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是不明白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.70,0:11:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說  你到底在期待些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.85,0:11:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  這裡是醫院  我還是傷員啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.45,0:11:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  這裡可是有許多精密儀器的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.70,0:11:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.09,0:12:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天晚上  御阪妹妹來過了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.71,0:12:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說實驗中止了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.05,0:12:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.74,0:12:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我的錯  很多的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.74,0:12:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你沒有提供DNA圖譜的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.85,0:12:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹們就不會誕生到這個世界上來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.85,0:12:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(215,332)\fs16\fsp1}Sisters
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.53,0:12:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然那個實驗有很多不對的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.00,0:12:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但唯獨妹妹們的誕生這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.00,0:12:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(295,332)\fs16\fsp1}Sisters
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.89,0:12:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得是你值得驕傲的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.73,0:12:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為如果她們沒有出生的話  就無法體會到快樂和悲傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.62,0:12:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且她們肯定也…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.54,0:13:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想看到你一個人獨自煩惱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.41,0:13:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}玩什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.07,0:13:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你傷勢怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.31,0:13:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那個少年相比不值一提
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.32,0:13:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.84,0:13:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要推了喲  來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.90,0:13:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機器製造出來的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.42,0:13:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛出生的她們如同一張白紙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.67,0:13:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以只要向她們灌輸自己是實驗動物的思想的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.22,0:13:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們就會接受自己的價值
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.80,0:13:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果像那傢伙一樣  周圍的人也將她們作為一個人來看待的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.67,0:13:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些孩子們肯定也…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.55,0:13:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:14:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們肯定不想見到我  也不會原諒我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.79,0:14:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你們今後要被社會接納難以避免會遇到困難
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.11,0:14:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.97,0:14:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有什麼我可以幫忙…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.73,0:14:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.87,0:14:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這叫做站立鞦韆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.85,0:14:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御阪把從學習裝置得到的知識進行實踐  並和風融為了一體
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.85,0:14:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(203,332)\fs16\fsp0}Testament
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.85,0:14:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.39,0:14:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼  再繼續下去的話可能會影響傷勢  所以就到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.47,0:14:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御阪擦著汗說道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.69,0:14:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.81,0:14:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  暫時不要管我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.96,0:14:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.01,0:14:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  我不要嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.58,0:14:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.85,0:14:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為姐姐就有要聽從妹妹任性要求的義務
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.97,0:15:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御阪對幼苗進行洗腦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.05,0:15:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.83,0:15:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這叫做小貓喲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.45,0:15:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.24,0:15:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐你們是姐妹嗎  長得一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.48,0:15:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙胞胎嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.53,0:15:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰是姐姐  誰是妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.13,0:15:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉璃自己來猜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.93,0:15:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.67,0:15:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.67,0:15:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是自己提出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.74,0:15:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.06,0:15:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊的姐姐是妹妹吧  因為她有呱太
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.35,0:15:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉璃也有玩偶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.74,0:15:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御阪做出笑噴的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.03,0:15:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她確實擁有和年齡不符的幼稚愛好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.18,0:15:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粗魯  急性子  動不動就發火
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.25,0:16:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此是個沒法袒露自己心聲的傲嬌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.26,0:16:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也是個為了御阪能夠不顧自己性命的令人頭疼的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.34,0:16:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.10,0:16:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御阪明明就應該在昨晚的實驗中死去的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.57,0:16:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是重複了一萬次以上理所當然的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.25,0:16:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但現在這個瞬間我卻還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.48,0:16:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御阪們是為了被殺而製造出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.57,0:16:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們唯一的存在價值  也是被製造出來的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.49,0:16:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但因為姐姐和那個少年的原因  這個目的消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.22,0:17:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裁員  失業  露宿街頭中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.45,0:17:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  為了能讓御阪找到生存的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.76,0:17:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後請和御阪一起去尋找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.37,0:17:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御阪提出了自己最任性的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.68,0:17:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.05,0:17:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.40,0:17:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.08,0:17:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  是那麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.53,0:17:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.78,0:17:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御阪學姐她啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.82,0:18:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為宿舍的廚房人多不好辦事所以來借我家的烤箱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.57,0:18:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞得雞飛狗跳的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.63,0:18:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以變成這副慘狀了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.45,0:18:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺真是意外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.01,0:18:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.18,0:18:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過御阪學姐終於打起精神真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.18,0:18:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.31,0:18:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但到底是要送給誰的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.49,0:18:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這無論我怎麼問她都不肯說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.26,0:18:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.28,0:18:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  佐天同學儘是開我玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.46,0:18:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是喜歡才做的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.58,0:18:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是謝禮  謝禮！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.16,0:18:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但反正是那個傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.62,0:18:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我是在為了自己戰鬥  沒什麼值得你道謝的」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.64,0:18:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會這麼說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.48,0:18:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是畫蛇添足了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.31,0:18:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  如果他要那麼說的話  要道謝什麼的也是我的自由啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.85,0:19:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說讓我親手去做曲奇  他敢不收的話我可不會輕易…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.73,0:19:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼是免費的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.96,0:19:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.88,0:19:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不應該還在住院的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊  住院費實在是有點貴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.10,0:19:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外餓肚子的同居人也變得日益凶殘了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.14,0:19:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說你才是呢  在這種地方幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.69,0:19:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.44,0:19:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是又來探望我了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.56,0:19:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.97,0:19:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.56,0:19:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不用這麼全力否定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.07,0:19:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.47,0:19:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是來探望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.08,0:19:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的事你幫了不少忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.14,0:19:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.26,0:19:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.32,0:19:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.84,0:19:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.04,0:20:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.03,0:20:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.28,0:20:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螞蟻？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.80,0:20:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做自由研究嗎  暑假也快要結束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.11,0:20:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  話說你當我是小學生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.28,0:20:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思打擾你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.83,0:20:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了  辟里啪啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.70,0:20:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御阪美琴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.32,0:20:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.74,0:20:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.67,0:20:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是辟里啪啦  是御阪美琴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.19,0:20:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了好幾遍了  你也該記住了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.40,0:20:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過可能也只是對牛彈琴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.15,0:20:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了  御阪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.79,0:21:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了  姐姐大…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.44,0:21:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底怎麼了  姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.99,0:21:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體不舒服嗎    哪兒受傷了嗎  還是說吃了什麼髒東西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.62,0:21:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊  話說什麼事情糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.82,0:21:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的無故留宿在外的事情被舍監發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.09,0:21:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她要求做出可以接受的解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.59,0:21:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真糟糕了  得找個借口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.89,0:21:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是為了說這個特地過來的啊  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.76,0:21:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你怎麼知道我在這兒的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.15,0:21:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人的事我最瞭解了  有姐姐大人的地方就有黑子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.84,0:21:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那個  真的沒發生什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.94,0:21:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果姐姐大人有個萬一  黑子也不能坐視…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.96,0:21:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你再說些有的沒的  我可就要扔下你不管了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.70,0:21:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是姐姐大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.28,0:22:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做出那種我從來沒有見到過的表情
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.62,0:23:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御阪學姐能重新打起精神真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.19,0:23:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那餅乾到底是為誰烤的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.98,0:23:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光溜溜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.69,0:23:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白井同學
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.37,0:23:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學習會的黑子一絲不掛
